<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَتَظَاهَرُوا وَتَجَمَّعُوا تَحْتَ الْجَلِيدْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هَتَفُوا لَهَا ... حَنُّوا لَهَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكَأَنَّهَا طِفْلٌ وَلِيدْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>هَلْ يَسْمَعَنْ أَحَدٌ بِأَنَّ الْيَوْمَ يُبْكَى مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَمْ مِنْ نِسَائِكَ ذَبَّحُوا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَوْ هُتِّكَتْ أَعْرَاضُهُنَّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>كَذَا الرِّجَالْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>كَمْ مِنْ رَضِيعٍ يُذْبَحُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوَمَا رَأَيْتَ بِشَاشَةِ التِّلْفَازِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كَيْفَ يَسِيلُ بَحْرٌ مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَنَهَارُ يَوْمِكَ مُظْلِمٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِمَّا غَشَاهُ مِنْ هَوَانِكَ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كُلَّ يَوْمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>